Account Deletion Instructions

Steps to delete your account and associated data:

1 - Open the app.

2 - Go to Account Settings (from the Profile or Settings menu).

3 - Tap Delete Account.

4 - Confirm your choice.

Your account and all associated data will be permanently deleted from our servers.

If you no longer have access to the app, you can also request account deletion by contacting us at lectio@gmail.com with the subject line “Account Deletion Request”.
We will verify your identity and delete your account and associated data within [X days, e.g. 30 days].
